BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 104.64 600 Td (Chapter 1: What is a Podcast?) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (A podcast is an audio show that people can listen to anytime, anywhere.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Think of it like a radio show that listeners download or stream on demand.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Podcasts are free to create and free for listeners to enjoy.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (There are over four million podcasts covering every topic imaginable.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Listeners subscribe and automatically receive new episodes when published.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (People listen during commutes, workouts, cooking, and before sleep.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Podcasts range from five-minute daily shows to three-hour conversations.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (You can podcast solo, with a co-host, or by interviewing guests.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (The barrier to entry is low: a microphone and free software is all you need.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Podcasting builds deep connections with audiences unlike any other medium.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Many podcasters turn their shows into full-time careers and businesses.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (This book will guide you from idea to published episode step by step.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (1) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
