BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 100.80000000000001 600 Td (Chapter 3: Naming Your Podcast) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Your podcast name should clearly communicate what the show is about.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Include a keyword that helps people find you when searching for your topic.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Keep the name short, memorable, and easy to spell when heard aloud.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Avoid inside jokes, puns, or clever names that confuse new listeners.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Check that the name is not already taken on Apple Podcasts and Spotify.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Search for available domain names and social media handles to match.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Consider adding a subtitle that explains the show for clarity.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Example: The Budget Mom: Practical Tips for Saving Money Every Day.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Say the name out loud ten times. Does it feel natural and professional?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Ask friends and family if the name communicates what the show is about.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (You can always rebrand later but it is easier to choose well from the start.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Write down ten to twenty options and narrow down to your top three choices.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (3) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
