BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 70.08000000000001 600 Td (Chapter 9: Choosing a Hosting Platform) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (A podcast host stores your audio files and delivers them to all platforms.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (You cannot upload directly to Apple or Spotify. You need a hosting service.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Buzzsprout is beginner-friendly with a free plan for up to two hours monthly.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Anchor \(now Spotify for Podcasters\) is completely free with unlimited hosting.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Podbean offers affordable plans starting at nine dollars per month.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Libsyn is an industry standard trusted by professional podcasters.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Your host provides an RSS feed which is the URL that connects to all apps.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Consider features like analytics, website, monetization tools, and ease of use.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Upload your edited MP3 file, add episode title, description, and publish.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Most hosts also generate a basic website for your podcast automatically.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Reliable hosting ensures your episodes are always available to listeners.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Start with a free plan and upgrade as your audience and needs grow.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (9) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
