BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 66.24000000000001 600 Td (Chapter 10: Submitting to Apple/Spotify) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Apple Podcasts and Spotify together reach over 80 percent of podcast listeners.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Submit to Apple Podcasts through Apple Podcasts Connect at podcastsconnect.apple.com.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (You need an Apple ID to submit. Create a free one if you do not have one.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Paste your RSS feed URL from your hosting platform into the submission form.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Apple reviews new podcasts which takes between 24 hours and two weeks.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (For Spotify, submit through Spotify for Podcasters or your hosting platform.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Most hosting platforms like Buzzsprout can submit to Spotify for you automatically.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Also submit to Google Podcasts, Amazon Music, and iHeartRadio for full coverage.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Have at least one episode published before submitting to directories.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Some podcasters launch with three episodes so new listeners have content immediately.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Once approved, your podcast is available to millions of potential listeners.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Check that your show appears correctly with proper artwork and descriptions.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 211.2 30 Td (10) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
