BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 89.28 600 Td (Chapter 12: Growing Your Audience) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Consistency is the number one factor in podcast growth. Publish on schedule.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Choose a realistic schedule: weekly is ideal but biweekly works too.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Ask listeners to subscribe and leave reviews at the end of every episode.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Share new episodes on all your social media platforms consistently.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Create short audio or video clips from episodes to share on social media.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Guest on other podcasts in your niche to reach new audiences.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Invite guests who have their own audience and will share the episode.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Engage with listeners through social media, email, and community groups.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Collaborate with other podcasters for cross-promotion episodes.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Optimize your show title and descriptions with searchable keywords.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Ask listeners what topics they want covered and deliver on their requests.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Growth is slow at first. Most successful podcasts took one to two years to build.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 211.2 30 Td (12) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
