BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Three weeks before: purchase and set up your recording equipment.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Two weeks before: record and edit your first three episodes.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Ten days before: set up your hosting account and upload episodes.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (One week before: submit your RSS feed to Apple Podcasts and Spotify.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Five days before: write show notes and create social media announcements.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Three days before: tell friends and family about your launch date.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Launch day: publish all three episodes and announce everywhere.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Ask everyone you know to subscribe, listen, and leave a review.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (First week: share daily on social media and engage with any feedback.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (First month: publish on your consistent schedule without missing a week.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Celebrate your launch! Most people talk about starting but never actually do it.) Tj ET
